1
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:29,719
=Soft-Hearted God=

2
00:00:29,720 --> 00:00:33,895
=Episode 19=
(What is love,)

3
00:00:34,025 --> 00:00:37,520
(that it binds us beyond death?)

4
00:00:51,380 --> 00:00:52,620
Zhao.

5
00:00:55,820 --> 00:00:56,820
Zhao?

6
00:01:04,540 --> 00:01:05,300
Xi.

7
00:01:10,500 --> 00:01:12,020
Zhao.

8
00:01:13,340 --> 00:01:18,300
I have found the cure
for the Verdant Decay.

9
00:01:19,380 --> 00:01:22,700
They will no longer suffer.

10
00:01:22,780 --> 00:01:24,020
The cure?

11
00:01:24,820 --> 00:01:26,020
Yes.

12
00:01:27,100 --> 00:01:28,460
Honey,

13
00:01:28,660 --> 00:01:30,900
you are the cure.

14
00:01:32,860 --> 00:01:33,780
No.

15
00:01:34,020 --> 00:01:34,860
No!

16
00:01:35,380 --> 00:01:37,700
Hua Hui, come back!

17
00:01:37,740 --> 00:01:39,420
If you dare harm Zhao,

18
00:01:39,460 --> 00:01:41,020
I will die with you!

19
00:01:41,060 --> 00:01:42,259
Shut up.

20
00:01:42,260 --> 00:01:43,179
Watch closely.

21
00:01:43,180 --> 00:01:44,660
Just come at me!

22
00:01:58,740 --> 00:02:02,420
I have found the cure for this illness.

23
00:02:05,460 --> 00:02:06,780
Look!

24
00:02:07,060 --> 00:02:08,379
Her vile plant has fallen off.

25
00:02:08,380 --> 00:02:09,780
She's still alive.

26
00:02:09,980 --> 00:02:11,420
How did she recover?

27
00:02:11,620 --> 00:02:12,619
Save us, please!

28
00:02:12,620 --> 00:02:14,339
Have Bai and Hua been cured too?

29
00:02:14,340 --> 00:02:15,259
Save the children.

30
00:02:15,260 --> 00:02:16,420
Save us, please.

31
00:02:17,340 --> 00:02:18,179
I want to live too.

32
00:02:18,180 --> 00:02:19,339
Hua and Bai are dead.

33
00:02:19,340 --> 00:02:21,020
The root-severing rite has failed.

34
00:02:22,100 --> 00:02:23,539
What shall we do?

35
00:02:23,540 --> 00:02:24,699
Yes, what should we do?

36
00:02:24,700 --> 00:02:25,899
How did Lady He recover?

37
00:02:25,900 --> 00:02:27,140
Everyone.

38
00:02:28,620 --> 00:02:32,220
Zhao's flesh and blood
can cure this illness.

39
00:02:33,180 --> 00:02:33,899
Flesh and blood?

40
00:02:33,900 --> 00:02:35,259
How could she ask us

41
00:02:35,260 --> 00:02:36,339
to harm her husband?

42
00:02:36,340 --> 00:02:37,339
Is that true?

43
00:02:37,340 --> 00:02:38,619
Doesn't that make us a beast?

44
00:02:38,620 --> 00:02:40,060
I believe Xi.

45
00:02:41,620 --> 00:02:42,339
I'll try.

46
00:02:42,340 --> 00:02:44,420
Chief Zhang? He...

47
00:02:46,180 --> 00:02:49,899
(Cutie, this is your people.)

48
00:02:49,900 --> 00:02:52,339
(No one is truly innocent.)

49
00:02:52,340 --> 00:02:53,059
Zhang Muzhi.

50
00:02:53,060 --> 00:02:54,339
Zhang Muzhi, stop it!

51
00:02:54,340 --> 00:02:55,660
Don't touch him!

52
00:02:58,940 --> 00:03:01,060
Chief Zhang really bit him.

53
00:03:01,660 --> 00:03:02,780
How could he...

54
00:03:16,180 --> 00:03:17,419
Chief Zhang is really cured.

55
00:03:17,420 --> 00:03:18,499
I am cured.

56
00:03:18,500 --> 00:03:19,619
I am really cured.

57
00:03:19,620 --> 00:03:22,180
Everyone, what Xi said is true.

58
00:03:23,820 --> 00:03:25,099
There are so many of us.

59
00:03:25,100 --> 00:03:26,219
He will die.

60
00:03:26,220 --> 00:03:26,819
Yeah.

61
00:03:26,820 --> 00:03:28,499
No, we cannot do this.

62
00:03:28,500 --> 00:03:29,579
If we do, we'll become murderers.

63
00:03:29,580 --> 00:03:31,219
I heard he is a god, not a human.

64
00:03:31,220 --> 00:03:31,859
We cannot do this.

65
00:03:31,860 --> 00:03:32,780
It should be fine.

66
00:03:35,340 --> 00:03:36,500
Everyone.

67
00:03:36,780 --> 00:03:37,859
Everyone,

68
00:03:37,860 --> 00:03:39,219
when this person first arrived,

69
00:03:39,220 --> 00:03:41,299
he killed Butcher Zhang's entire family.

70
00:03:41,300 --> 00:03:44,340
Life for life.
It's the way of the world.

71
00:03:45,140 --> 00:03:47,459
We must make him pay with his life!

72
00:03:47,460 --> 00:03:48,900
Pay with his life.

73
00:03:49,020 --> 00:03:50,460
Pay with his life.

74
00:03:52,060 --> 00:03:53,459
We must avenge Butcher Zhang!

75
00:03:53,460 --> 00:03:54,659
Avenge Butcher Zhang!

76
00:03:54,660 --> 00:03:55,459
Pay with his life!

77
00:03:55,460 --> 00:03:56,939
We must avenge Butcher Zhang!

78
00:03:56,940 --> 00:03:58,940
Avenge Butcher Zhang!

79
00:04:02,660 --> 00:04:04,380
We shall execute justice!

80
00:04:19,180 --> 00:04:20,340
Bai,

81
00:04:20,780 --> 00:04:24,940
I feel much lighter now.

82
00:04:27,780 --> 00:04:29,459
Judging from your pulse,

83
00:04:29,460 --> 00:04:31,059
it seems you're cured too.

84
00:04:31,060 --> 00:04:32,499
We need to tell Lady He.

85
00:04:32,500 --> 00:04:33,900
Don't waste any more time.

86
00:04:42,087 --> 00:04:44,807
(What should those with the vile plant)

87
00:04:45,020 --> 00:04:47,220
(growing near their vital parts do?)

88
00:05:08,420 --> 00:05:12,620
Killing a god can gain immortality.

89
00:05:19,420 --> 00:05:21,540
(No, I can't do that.)

90
00:05:24,540 --> 00:05:27,099
(If we are to live,
we shall live together.)

91
00:05:27,100 --> 00:05:28,740
(If we are to die...)

92
00:05:29,900 --> 00:05:32,620
(then we die together.)

93
00:05:42,060 --> 00:05:43,099
It's the way of the world.

94
00:05:43,100 --> 00:05:45,100
Avenge Butcher Zhang.

95
00:05:45,220 --> 00:05:46,059
Execute justice.

96
00:05:46,060 --> 00:05:47,299
Forgive me.

97
00:05:47,300 --> 00:05:48,739
My mother, wife, and daughter

98
00:05:48,740 --> 00:05:50,179
are waiting for me to return home.

99
00:05:50,180 --> 00:05:51,059
I'll go first.

100
00:05:51,060 --> 00:05:52,179
Don't fight me for it.

101
00:05:52,180 --> 00:05:53,380
I'll go first.

102
00:05:53,460 --> 00:05:55,860
But avoid his vital points.

103
00:05:56,180 --> 00:05:57,539
We cannot let him die too quickly.

104
00:05:57,540 --> 00:05:59,180
If he dies, the blood won't work.

105
00:06:08,980 --> 00:06:10,979
No!

106
00:06:10,980 --> 00:06:12,620
Let him go!

107
00:06:13,420 --> 00:06:15,099
Let him go!

108
00:06:15,100 --> 00:06:16,660
Zhao!

109
00:06:18,540 --> 00:06:20,099
(Cutie,)

110
00:06:20,100 --> 00:06:21,860
(this is what it means to be human.)

111
00:06:21,980 --> 00:06:23,859
(With just a little provocation,)

112
00:06:23,860 --> 00:06:25,979
(they'll all rush in.)

113
00:06:25,980 --> 00:06:27,419
(To survive,)

114
00:06:27,420 --> 00:06:29,940
(they will do anything.)

115
00:06:30,540 --> 00:06:32,100
Zhao!

116
00:07:03,620 --> 00:07:05,940
Xi, it hurts.

117
00:07:06,540 --> 00:07:08,820
Xi, it hurts so much.

118
00:07:12,420 --> 00:07:13,860
Xi.

119
00:07:15,940 --> 00:07:17,300
It hurts so much.

120
00:07:19,100 --> 00:07:20,620
Why?

121
00:07:21,300 --> 00:07:22,420
It hurts.

122
00:07:24,860 --> 00:07:25,940
It hurts.

123
00:07:28,100 --> 00:07:29,620
Why?

124
00:07:35,500 --> 00:07:37,300
Why?

125
00:07:50,980 --> 00:07:52,180
Because...

126
00:07:54,060 --> 00:07:56,500
I am a demon.

127
00:07:58,220 --> 00:08:00,620
My soft-hearted god.

128
00:08:36,180 --> 00:08:39,260
It's all my fault.

129
00:08:39,380 --> 00:08:40,619
Zhao!

130
00:08:40,620 --> 00:08:42,099
Cutie,

131
00:08:42,100 --> 00:08:43,740
don't be sad.

132
00:08:44,420 --> 00:08:46,740
A god cannot be revived once dead.

133
00:08:47,420 --> 00:08:49,099
I'll let you out,

134
00:08:49,100 --> 00:08:50,860
so you can see for yourself

135
00:08:51,540 --> 00:08:55,420
what your husband
has become because of you.

136
00:09:18,100 --> 00:09:19,300
I'm sorry.

137
00:09:21,900 --> 00:09:23,300
I'm sorry.

138
00:09:23,860 --> 00:09:26,140
I'm so sorry.

139
00:09:26,860 --> 00:09:28,220
I beg you.

140
00:09:28,580 --> 00:09:29,739
I beg you.

141
00:09:29,740 --> 00:09:31,300
Come back to life.

142
00:09:31,380 --> 00:09:33,300
Come back to life.

143
00:09:33,820 --> 00:09:35,099
Tell me.

144
00:09:35,100 --> 00:09:36,540
Tell me.

145
00:09:36,740 --> 00:09:38,660
What should I do?

146
00:09:39,980 --> 00:09:41,220
What should I do?

147
00:09:45,100 --> 00:09:47,420
(Can my blood...)

148
00:10:03,020 --> 00:10:04,140
Why?

149
00:10:05,460 --> 00:10:06,580
Why?

150
00:10:06,740 --> 00:10:08,220
Why is it not working?

151
00:10:13,350 --> 00:10:19,200
♪It bids farewell to another blue sky♪

152
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:21,511
♪To meet is to overlap♪

153
00:10:21,512 --> 00:10:23,486
♪To see is to part again♪

154
00:10:23,487 --> 00:10:26,259
♪To stay is to wish for forever♪

155
00:10:26,260 --> 00:10:28,060
Why?

156
00:10:28,260 --> 00:10:30,540
Why is it not working?

157
00:10:34,220 --> 00:10:36,099
He has lost his divine heart.

158
00:10:36,100 --> 00:10:37,499
He is now a mortal.

159
00:10:37,500 --> 00:10:40,060
Your blood, of course, has no effect.

160
00:10:42,275 --> 00:10:45,219
♪Soaking these hazy, drowsy eyes♪

161
00:10:45,220 --> 00:10:46,540
Who are you?

162
00:10:46,860 --> 00:10:48,180
Heavenly Dao.

163
00:10:48,980 --> 00:10:52,780
I have returned
my divine heart to Heavenly Dao.

164
00:10:52,912 --> 00:10:55,907
♪So I'm afraid of goodbye♪

165
00:10:57,380 --> 00:11:00,060
I beg you.

166
00:11:00,380 --> 00:11:02,579
Please return his divine heart to him.

167
00:11:02,580 --> 00:11:04,339
It was always his.

168
00:11:04,340 --> 00:11:05,859
Naturally, it must be returned to him.

169
00:11:05,860 --> 00:11:07,979
But his flesh and blood
that have been consumed...

170
00:11:07,980 --> 00:11:11,020
Use mine.

171
00:11:12,220 --> 00:11:13,820
Use mine.

172
00:11:14,100 --> 00:11:15,900
This will cost you your life.

173
00:11:16,020 --> 00:11:17,579
You must think carefully.

174
00:11:17,580 --> 00:11:21,739
♪If in a dream, I can hear your voice♪

175
00:11:21,740 --> 00:11:23,900
This should not be his end.

176
00:11:26,620 --> 00:11:27,986
I will save him.

177
00:11:27,987 --> 00:11:32,357
♪Drawing endlessly close♪

178
00:11:50,100 --> 00:11:52,099
Once the divine heart is destroyed

179
00:11:52,100 --> 00:11:54,140
or used by another,

180
00:11:54,500 --> 00:11:58,140
Ye Zhao will never
have a chance at rebirth.

181
00:11:58,620 --> 00:12:00,540
You must think carefully.

182
00:12:01,587 --> 00:12:03,449
♪Even if reluctant, what can be done♪

183
00:12:03,450 --> 00:12:05,424
♪Chasing something always out of reach♪

184
00:12:05,425 --> 00:12:08,759
♪So I'm afraid of goodbye♪

185
00:12:08,760 --> 00:12:14,219
♪Living the same day
over and over again♪

186
00:12:14,220 --> 00:12:15,940
(Perhaps, if I reincarnate,)

187
00:12:16,500 --> 00:12:18,580
(I can rid myself of this demon heart.)

188
00:12:20,700 --> 00:12:23,060
(I will definitely
come back to find you.)

189
00:12:24,020 --> 00:12:26,020
(You must wait for me.)

190
00:12:30,137 --> 00:12:31,736
♪If in a dream♪

191
00:12:31,737 --> 00:12:34,496
♪I can hear your voice♪

192
00:12:34,497 --> 00:12:37,346
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

193
00:12:37,347 --> 00:12:39,946
♪Let it be us♪

194
00:12:39,947 --> 00:12:44,757
♪drawing endlessly close♪

195
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:01,759
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

196
00:13:01,760 --> 00:13:04,410
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

197
00:13:04,630 --> 00:13:07,349
♪I can't even hold you properly♪

198
00:13:07,350 --> 00:13:08,999
♪Not even in time♪

199
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:14,659
♪to tell you how I feel♪

200
00:13:14,660 --> 00:13:16,199
♪If the rain won't stop♪

201
00:13:16,200 --> 00:13:18,949
♪If the wind won't fade,
if time stands still♪

202
00:13:18,950 --> 00:13:21,919
♪Let love go on♪

203
00:13:21,920 --> 00:13:24,469
♪Until forever♪

204
00:13:24,470 --> 00:13:29,109
♪Until we slowly grow old♪

205
00:13:29,110 --> 00:13:31,719
♪Until forever♪

206
00:13:31,720 --> 00:13:38,830
♪Until we slowly grow old♪
